Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:01:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is today the last day of Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of cute cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not really interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Okarin's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said we weren't doing the cracking, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's gonna reach a high of 35!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hydration is the best way to prevent heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to Comima today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really sunny out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}August 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.48,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each D-mail I undid delayed Mayuri's death by one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:19.94,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fscx86}Erasing Suzuha's mail made the events of the 13th occur on the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.65,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feyris, Rukako, Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:26.16,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each one pushed it back a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:30.54,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then in this world line, Mayuri dies on the 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.12,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, before 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost sold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one for Daru-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there was a book on a \Nrobot anime I thought you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if there's anywhere you'd like to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to think about, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Organization assassins hiding in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something to escape their clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful, they might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the original plan until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think any bad people like that are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet back here at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're selling juice over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before that time, find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way for her to survive without changing world lines.
