Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at the second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously having you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we haven't touched it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain what's going on, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri will die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're doing the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To erase the first D-mail you sent{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to think of a way to save \NMayuri without the cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have changed. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I won't be able to think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to stop by the lab, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii was thinking of getting some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Almost time for her to die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. That never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely went to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted to check something out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've shown you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many things Mayushii knows more than Okarin about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never gone to Comima together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Mayushii was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see Rukako looking embarrassed in his cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if he had, he would've been really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Ruka-kun would have gotten his photo on all the blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he'd have become a worldwide superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Mayushii would have seen it and said, "He's come a long way."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be even better if Okarin cosplayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, you'd also have to cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... We'll call Rukako and Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can convince them to cosplay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, then I,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma, mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall make my cosplay debut at Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kurisu-chan was interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Mayushii will try her best to do it by the next Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My watch isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't go through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stop it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I let that car hit me... If I die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something has to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally, I was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii was useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see the stars from here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.26,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\frx18\fry6\frz336.998\move(921,543,772,542,0,2444)\fsp-3}I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.26,Writing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\frx16\fry0\frz332.027\move(870,652,720,652,0,2444)\fsp-3}Kurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been up here, on the roof, for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without a sound. I got worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm not worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yourself said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought the FBI would come, and you got scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to be thought of as a law-abiding citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your normal, hotshot attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I act like that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew within five seconds of meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you time leap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've helped you with everything so far, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made it this far by thinking things through together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha and Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrificed the things they loved the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, this is how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, you were crying back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida was concerned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought maybe you had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri and I went to \NDr. Nakabachi's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I saw Makise Kurisu collapsed after being stabbed by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent a text to Daru's cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was connected to the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message that moved us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the beta world line to the alpha world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting that message from SERN's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means going back to that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we return to the beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daru-kun told me you were acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii's been so busy with Comima,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she couldn't spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you used to talk to Mayushii about all kinds of stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were four Organization generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geppu, Sudachi, Seiyuu, and Jakkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genbu, Suzaku, Seiryuu, Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked hearing about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mayushii is ever a burden, tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mayushii can do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From your voice, I can guess what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to come up with any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you do stay here, talking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were sitting here alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should go see Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that will happen if you stay and worry is that you'll hurt my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii. I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the cosplayers said Mayushii left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.80,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see me because it's Obon, right, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.97,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only been having scary dreams lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:06.06,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dreams, terrible things happen to Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets shot with a pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or she's in a car accident or run over by a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything seems like it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary, and it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to scream for help, as loud as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the end of the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin always comes to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii says, "Thank you, Okarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't hear her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He holds Mayushii, and he looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he never cries, but you can tell he really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii says, "I'm sorry." But he doesn't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, there are lots of new lab members!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Moeka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ruka-kun, and Feyris-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan is super-smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she talks about all these really hard things with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin looks happy that he gets to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, sometimes I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time Mayushii went to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the beginning of spring, but it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to the lab after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was cleaning up the room, he came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't say, "I'm back."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, every day after that, I'd go there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.81,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,for about two hours, and we'd barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.44,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't bad. We were simply there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:27.41,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passed so slowly, and it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:32.00,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii thought she really was like a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing good happened, but it was good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand... You saw some kind of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may be an attack by \NOrganization General Illusion Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I bet that Illusion Contactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:20:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think he's a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I haven't spent much time talking with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be that when I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's really suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he's always about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know he's thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I was talking about something sad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mayushii's been lonely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, I can't stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always know where my hostage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't ever escape from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hououin Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am not so weak that I need you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes that I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get another Upa gatchapon, right?

